sentences.en: It seems Pandora is the only place in the galaxy with deposits of a valuable new energy source worth untold millions back on Earth.

sentences.en: When Pandora closed the box in fear, she heard a little voice calling: "Let me out!" When she asked who the voice was, the answer was: "I am Hope!"

sentences.en: I 'm not in Kansas anymore. I am in Pandora.
